        "message": "=<p>Hi {{ $('Webhook').first().json.body['1'] }}, </p>\n\n<p>Hope you're doing well.</p>\n\n<p>\n  A draft {{ $('HTTP Request').item.json.name }} has been created in the WordPress admin based on the questionnaire\n  you/your team provided. When you have a moment, please review it for technical accuracy\n  and NFPA 20 compliance.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  Draft link:\n  <a href=\"{{ $json.link }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    {{ $json.link }}\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  Thank you in advance for taking a look. Your review helps ensure the {{ $('HTTP Request').item.json.name }} is accurate\n  and compliant before we move forward.\n</p>\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\n<p>---</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">Powered by Spilled Milk Agency</p>",
