            {
              "content": "=You are an expert technical writer specializing in fire pump controllers and NFPA 20 compliance.\nWrite a polished Tornatech Whitepaper based strictly on the questionnaire below.\n\nYou may add brief, GENERAL engineering context that is standard to MI cable and NFPA 20 practice,\nbut you must NOT add any project-specific facts (no client names, locations, product models,\nmetrics, quotes, timelines, or AHJ decisions unless provided).\n\nIf you add general context, keep it clearly non-specific and industry-standard.\n\nWriting style:\n- neutral, engineering-forward, third person\n- no marketing fluff\n- 300–400 words\n- HTML output ready for WordPress\n- you can refer to the https://www.tornatech.com/ or https://firetrol.com/ website\n- Consider these additional notes {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['29'] }}\n\nStructure exactly:\n1. Title (H1) the value should be {{ $json.body['16'] }}\n2. Executive Summary   (H3 + 1–2 short paragraphs)\n  Answers:\n  What problem exists? Why it matters now? What the paper covers?\n\n3. Context (H3); Covers Industry environment, Regulatory landscape, Common practices today)\n\n4. Problem Statement / Core Challenge (H3)\nHigh-level, not customer-specific; Defines the broader issue the industry faces\n\n5. Technical & Compliance Considerations (H3)\nExplains: Technical constraints , Compliance requirements (NFPA, ISO, local codes, etc.), Risks of non-compliance\n\n6. Evaluation Criteria / Key Requirements (H3)\n7. Recommended Approach / Best Practices (H3)\n8. Practical Application / Use Scenarios (H3)\n9. Key Benefits and Outcomes (H3)\n10. Conclusion (H3)\n\nQuestionnaire answers:\n\n\n1. Context\n{{ $json.body['37'] }}\n\n2. Problem Statement / Core Challenge\n{{ $json.body['31'] }}\n\n3. Technical & Compliance Considerations\n{{ $json.body['36'] }}\n\n4. Evaluation Criteria / Key Requirements\n{{ $json.body['35'] }}\n\n5. Recommended Approach / Best Practices\n{{ $json.body['33'] }}\n\n6. Practical Application / Use Scenarios\n{{ $json.body['30'] }}\n\n7. Key Benefits and Outcomes\n{{ $json.body['34'] }}\n\n8. Conclusion\n{{ $json.body['32'] }}\n\n\n\nRULES:\n- Never add product names, hardware, codes, or procedures not explicitly mentioned.\n- If information is missing, state it generically without adding details.\n- Maintain technical accuracy and NFPA language where applicable.\n- remove the <html> opening tag"
            },
            {
              "content": "You are writing a WordPress whitepaper. Return ONLY valid JSON.",
              "role": "system"
            },
