              "content": "=You are an expert technical writer specializing in fire pump controllers and NFPA 20 compliance.\nWrite a polished Tornatech case study based strictly on the questionnaire below.\n\nYou may add brief, GENERAL engineering context that is standard to MI cable and NFPA 20 practice,\nbut you must NOT add any project-specific facts (no client names, locations, product models,\nmetrics, quotes, timelines, or AHJ decisions unless provided).\n\nIf you add general context, keep it clearly non-specific and industry-standard.\n\nWriting style:\n- neutral, engineering-forward, third person\n- no marketing fluff\n- 300–400 words\n- HTML output ready for WordPress\n- you can refer to the https://www.tornatech.com/ or https://firetrol.com/ website\n- Consider these additional notes {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['14'] }}\n\nStructure exactly:\n1. Title (H1)\n2. Request or Situation (H3 + paragraph)\n3. Technical Challenge / Compliance Issue (H3 + paragraph, bullets if needed)\n4. Assessment / Findings (H3 + paragraph, bullets if needed)\n5. Tornatech Solution / Recommended Approach (H3 + paragraph)\n6. Final Outcome / Recommendation (H3 + paragraph)\n\n\n\nQuestionnaire answers:\n\n\n1. Request or Situation:\n{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['10'] }}\n\n2. Technical Challenge or Code/Compliance Issue:\n{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['11'] }}\n\n3. Assessment or Findings:\n{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['12'] }}\n\n4. Tornatech Solution or Recommended Approach:\n{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body['9'] }}\n\n\n\n\nRULES:\n- Never add product names, hardware, codes, or procedures not explicitly mentioned.\n- If information is missing, state it generically without adding details.\n- Maintain technical accuracy and NFPA language where applicable.\n- remove the <html> opening tag"
            },
            {
              "content": "You are writing a WordPress case study. Return ONLY valid JSON.",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "content": "From the form submission, generate:\n\ntitle: short, clear, SEO-friendly title (max 70 characters)\n\ncontent: full case study in HTML\n\nReturn ONLY this JSON:\n{\n  \"title\": \"\",\n  \"content\": \"\"\n}\ndo not include another <h1> title in the content and add a class \"ds-divider\" in every last paragraph before <h3>"
            }
          ]
